
#2 --------------------------------------------------------------------

for concardis.py:convertCurrency:

get historical currency exchange rates. Sources:
 - ichart.yahoo.com/table.csv?s=EURUSD=X (has 2-3 months gaps)
 - http://www.ecb.europa.eu/stats/eurofxref/eurofxref-hist-90d.xml (only contains 28 currencies)

